snippet: AC Milan coach Clarence Seedorf and some of his players met a group of the team's ultra supporters to listen to their grievances following the 4-2 home defeat by Parma in Serie A on Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Milan Ultras Meet Players, Coach to Air Grievances
headline.main: Milan Ultras Meet Players, Coach to Air Grievances

lead_paragraph: AC Milan coach Clarence Seedorf and some of his players met a group of the team's ultra supporters to listen to their grievances following the 4-2 home defeat by Parma in Serie A on Sunday.
